{
  "id": "adv_event_2604_02_03",
  "title": "おさかな☆HEAVEN 3話 待ってて！ブリスケ！",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――それからしばらくして",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "ナレーション",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "地上に戻りいつも通りの生活を送っていた四人",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 2.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "ナレーション",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_02_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_02_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "しかし、雫はブリスケのことを忘れることが出来ません",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 8.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku Hyodo",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "みんなにお話があって集まってもらった……あのね……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku Hyodo",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_02_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_02_02-szk001.m4a",
      "text": "私、ブリスケを……助けに戻りたい！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 20.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura Kawasaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "戻るって『おさかな☆HEAVEN』に？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 24.4666670482,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura Kawasaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_02_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_02_02-skr001.m4a",
      "text": "私もブリスケのことは心配だけど、どうやって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 28.2666670482,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei Ichinose",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "雫の気持ちも分かる。でも、魚達の争いに人間の私達が",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 33.1666670482,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei Ichinose",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_02_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_02_02-rei001.m4a",
      "text": "首を突っ込んでも、出来ることなんて何もないと思う",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.8666670482,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei Ichinose",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "目を覚まして、雫。ブリスケは魚なのよ。なぜか人語を",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.2000003815,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei Ichinose",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_02_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_02_02-rei002.m4a",
      "text": "喋ってたけど私達がいつも食べてる魚と変わらないわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 49.8333337148,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku Hyodo",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "でも……お魚達が傷付け合ってるのを黙って見過ごす",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 54.5000003815,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku Hyodo",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_02_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_02_02-szk002.m4a",
      "text": "ことなんて出来ない。きっと話し合えば平和に――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 59.2333337148,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei Ichinose",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "雫……ごめんなさい、私とさくらは明日も仕事で",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 63.4000003815,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei Ichinose",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_02_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_02_02-rei003.m4a",
      "text": "朝が早いからもう部屋に戻るわね、おやすみ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 71.0666670482,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku Hyodo",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "怜ちゃん、さくらちゃん……！　一緒にブリスケを",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 76.7000003815,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 366.66628519999733
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 633.3329535999894
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku Hyodo",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_02_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_02_02-szk003.m4a",
      "text": "助けに行こう……！　明日の夕方、海岸で待ってる",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 81.5000003815,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa Shiraishi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "……雫ちゃん、何か私に手伝えること、ある？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 86.0333337148,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa Shiraishi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_02_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_02_02-chs001.m4a",
      "text": "私は雫ちゃんと一緒にブリスケを助けに行くよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 90.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku Hyodo",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "ありがとう……！　それじゃあお願いしたいことがある",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 94.4666670482,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku Hyodo",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_02_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_02_02-szk004.m4a",
      "text": "海に潜るためのウェットスーツを作って欲しい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 99.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――翌日",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 104.3333337148,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "ナレーション",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "昨晩、雫と千紗が寝る間も惜しんでチクチクと",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 106.3333316803,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "ナレーション",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_02_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_02_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "縫っていたウェットスーツはようやく完成しました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 110.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa Shiraishi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "てってれ～！　『まるでサカナスーツ』完成～！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 115.5000029247,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa Shiraishi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_02_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_02_02-chs002.m4a",
      "text": "魚魚っとさんからもらった布を使った特殊素材なんだよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 120.833337911,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa Shiraishi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "このスーツを着たらまるでお魚の見た目になれちゃうし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 125.6000029247,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa Shiraishi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_02_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_02_02-chs003.m4a",
      "text": "海の中でも呼吸が出来ちゃう特別な仕様なの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 129.6666712444,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku Hyodo",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "凄いよ、千紗ちゃん！　魚の姿だったら人間嫌いの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 133.8000029247,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku Hyodo",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_02_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_02_02-szk005.m4a",
      "text": "『オサカナ♦HELL』とも対話が出来るかも……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 138.2000045777,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――その日の夕方",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 142.0333474477,
      "sfxList": [
